極道梟雄 (freesynd-cht) — Licensing
===================================

This repository is a *localization record + patch set* for the 1993 Bullfrog
game *Syndicate*, built on the open-source FreeSynd engine. Different parts of
the repository are under different licenses. None of it contains EA's original
copyrighted game content (see README.md → "IP 乾淨設計").

1. Engine patches and tools  →  GPL-3.0-or-later
---------------------------------------------------
  patches/*.patch  and  tools/*.py  (and tools/*.cpp)
  are modifications to / utilities for FreeSynd, which is licensed
  GNU General Public License v3.0 or later. As derivative works they are
  likewise GPL-3.0-or-later. Each engine source file carries the GPLv3
  notice; the full text is at https://www.gnu.org/licenses/gpl-3.0.txt
  SPDX-License-Identifier: GPL-3.0-or-later

2. Bitmap fonts  →  SIL Open Font License 1.1
-----------------------------------------------
  fonts/chinese-12.fnt, fonts/chinese-16.fnt are bitmap glyph atlases
  rendered from Noto Sans CJK TC (© Google, SIL OFL-1.1). The derived
  bitmaps remain under OFL-1.1.
  SPDX-License-Identifier: OFL-1.1
  Full text: https://openfontlicense.org

3. Traditional-Chinese translations  →  personal / non-commercial
------------------------------------------------------------------
  data/lang/chinese-tw.lng              (functional UI strings — fair-use
                                         parallel to the engine's existing
                                         fr/de/it .lng files)
  translations_public/*.json            (briefing translations stored ONLY as
                                         FNV-1a-64 hashes of the original text
                                         + the zh rendering — the English is
                                         never stored)
  These are released for personal, non-commercial use with a copy of
  *Syndicate* you legally own. They reproduce no EA content; the original
  prose is recovered locally from the player's own game data via
  tools/apply_public.py.

4. Documentation  →  CC BY 4.0
-------------------------------
  README.md, docs/*.md, CONTEXT.md
  SPDX-License-Identifier: CC-BY-4.0

